{"tid":1883344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陷家剷！支那導演悲留遺言 一家4口17天內都辭世","createTime":"2020-02-17T01:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:16:27.000Z","uid":32511,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"27cc26aa1501f0ab5c9a71bdfb5f70f928f99da0","tid":1883344,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:16:49.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎肆虐全球，目前中國死亡人數已破1600人，湖北電影製片廠發布消息，其對外聯絡部主任常凱因此疾過世，享年55歲。先前有消息指出常凱全家人全去世，湖北電影製片廠發聲明證實常凱的死訊，其姐姐、父母也傳來噩耗，家中17天內4人相繼辭世。<br />\n <br />\n據微博及新浪娛樂消息，常凱也是導演，他兒子在英國留學未受波及，因武漢肺炎「幾乎滅門」，對抗過程非常艱辛，「作為一名導演尚且得不到床位，可以想像武漢的實際情況有多麼的慘烈。時代的一粒灰，只是僥倖沒有落在我們頭上」。微博也轉發著常凱導演遺言，「輾轉諸家醫院哀求哭拜，怎奈位卑言輕，床位難覓」，求助多方仍找不到床位，錯失黃金治療時機，最終不幸辭世。"},{"pid":"c6635f12630d871d77b20ae3405579e0e10c4092","tid":1883344,"uid":120070,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d0/Preview-8-2.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/340?cb=20100505085933\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd0%2FPreview-8-2.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F340%3Fcb%3D20100505085933&h=e6bdee25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8465d178d554486a41d72d54a84cd5d19e1a5fb","tid":1883344,"uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMyE7AZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMyE7AZ.gif&h=1857712f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8219113d86c7aeee0584c8989e240fb40d8a80e3","tid":1883344,"uid":125168,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teSKzgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteSKzgj.png&h=eef2bacd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9128703a8a71be063d5e5f77387522293ea5e56","tid":1883344,"uid":305544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re